{"word":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Wheat</b> General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=6&verse=6'>Rev 6:6</a><br/> Grown in Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=11'>1Ki 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=16'>Psa 81:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=147&verse=14'>Psa 147:14</a><br/> Offerings of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=12'>Num 18:12</a><br/> Prophecy of the sale of a measure of, for a penny<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=6&verse=6'>Rev 6:6</a><br/> Parables of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=25'>Mat 13:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=16&verse=7'>Luk 16:7</a><br/> Winnowing of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=12'>Mat 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=17'>Luk 3:17</a><br/> Ground in a mortar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=27&verse=22'>Pro 27:22</a><br/> Chaff of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=23&verse=28'>Jer 23:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=12'>Mat 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=17'>Luk 3:17</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of God's mercy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=16'>Psa 81:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=147&verse=14'>Psa 147:14</a> <br/> - Of self-righteousness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=12&verse=13'>Jer 12:13</a> <br/> - Growth of, figurative of vicarious death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=24'>Joh 12:24</a> "}]}